text:
What Are the Most Important Things Students Should Learn in School?

In your opinion, what are the most important things students should learn in school? What is the most important thing you have learned in school? How has this knowledge affected your life? How do you think it will help your success in the future?

---

In my opinion, the most important thing students should learn in school is right and wrong. I think that students should learn how to make good decisions and how to be a good person. It isn't an easy thing to teach though but it is one of the most valuable things in life. 

Another important thing that should be taught in schools is planning. I think that students should learn how to plan ahead and how to make a plan for the future. This is done by learning how to set goals and create planned steps.  This is good because teaches students how to be realistic and how to evaluate themselves. 

Teaching these things in schools offers students a good foundation for the future. It teaches them how to choose and direction and how to get themselves there. This can be applied to many different areas of life. It will help student successfully complete their studies. It will help them to be successful in their career. It will help them be successful in managing their finances. It will help them be successful in their relationships. And they can pass on this knowledge to other they live and work with. Every team can be better because of this.
